reviewText: The music in this video is just great, with all the bands playing.  I have had this movie for ten years and bought the most recent one for my eight month grand-daughter, this is her movie to listen and to fall asleep to.
Tuve la oportunidad de ver este homenaje al mariachi  a travs de la cadena KQED y es simplemete espectacular.  Recomiendo la cinta al 100%.
